                    'product introductions, product transitions, and SKU '
                    'rationalization. Ensure planning governance and '
                    'compliance with  pharma–cosmetics regulatory '
                    'requirements, internal policies, and operational '
                    'standards . 2. Planning Strategy & Execution Challenge '
                    'and validate  commercial demand assumptions , driving '
                    'improved forecast accuracy and demand visibility. Lead '
                    'structured  Demand Review and S&OP cycles , ensuring '
                    'timely and data-driven decision making across the '
                    'organization. Develop and manage  supply planning '
                    'strategies \xa0to ensure supply readiness while '
