                    'Business Analysis & Strategic Insights Deliver  advanced '
                    'planning analysis and actionable business insights \xa0to '
                    'support leadership decision-making. Monitor and drive '
                    'improvement in  planning performance metrics \xa0'
                    'including Forecast Accuracy, Bias, SMOS, and inventory '
                    'health indicators. Conduct  scenario modelling and '
                    'demand-supply simulations \xa0to evaluate business risks '
                    'and support strategic planning. Maintain clear visibility '
                    'across  demand, supply, and inventory performance \xa0'
                    'through structured reporting and analytics. 4. Leadership '
                    '& Functional Excellence Lead and develop the  Demand & '
